enhanced_by.reason: The isbnGs1() method provides the GS1 prefix required for constructing the ISBN13.
The isbnGroup() method provides the group identifier required for constructing the ISBN13.
The isbnRegistrant() method provides the registrant element required for constructing the ISBN13.
Both isbn10(boolean) and isbn13(boolean) generate ISBN numbers, allowing for similar assertions on their outputs.
The isbn13CheckDigit(CharSequence) method calculates the check digit for ISBN13, which can be used to assert the correctness of the generated ISBN13.
